OL,7,FA pensioner who preyed on vulnerable
OL,8,Fyoung women addicted to heroin by
OL,9,Ftrafficking them into prostitution is
OL,10,Fto have his prison sentence increased
OL,11,Fby two years, the Court of Appeal
OL,12,Fruled today.
OL,14,FSenior judges held that the seven-year
OL,15,Fterm originally handed down to Oliver
OL,16,FJames MacCormack, 72, was unduly
OL,17,Flenient.
