OL,3,CPensioner's sentence upped for
OL,4,Ctrafficking addicted women into
OL,5,Cprostitution
OL,7,FMacCormack previously admitted a total
OL,8,Fof 40 charges, including multiple
OL,9,Fcounts of human trafficking,
OL,10,Fcontrolling prostitution, supplying
OL,11,FClass A drugs, perverting the course
OL,12,Fof justice and witness intimidation.
OL,14,FThere were nine victims across the
OL,15,FGreater Belfast area, some aged as
OL,16,Fyoung as 17 when the offences were
OL,17,Fcommitted between 2015 and 2022.
OL,19,FOne of the women later died of sepsis
OL,20,Frelated to her drug use.
