OL,4,Ctrafficking addicted women into
OL,5,Cprostitution
OL,7,FMacCormack, from the Lisburn area,
OL,8,Ftargeted the victims by supplying them
OL,9,Fwith heroin to ensure they became
OL,10,Fdependent on him for their fixes.
OL,12,FThe court heard how he "ingratiated"
OL,13,Fhimself into their lives, grooming
OL,14,Fthem to become involved in sex work
OL,15,Fand arranging meetings with men
OL,16,Fwilling to pay for their services.
