OL,4,Ctrafficking addicted women into
OL,5,Cprostitution
OL,7,FCharles MacCreanor KC, for the PPS,
OL,8,Fargued that MacCormack manipulated and
OL,9,Fexploited young women who relied on
OL,10,Fhim for heroin.
OL,12,F"Ultimately he used them like
OL,13,Fcommodities to be sold in order to be
OL,14,Fof financial benefit," the barrister
OL,15,Fsubmitted.
OL,17,F"It was the most serious case seen in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland to date."
