OL,4,Ctrafficking addicted women into
OL,5,Cprostitution
OL,7,FDressed in jeans and a grey hoodie,
OL,8,FMacCormack was escorted into court in
OL,9,Fhandcuffs by prison guards for the
OL,10,Fappeal hearing.
OL,12,FSome of his victims sat nearby in the
OL,13,Fpublic gallery throughout the
OL,14,Fproceedings.
OL,16,FBacking the PPS case, the three appeal
OL,17,Fjudges formally declared that the
OL,18,Fsentence was unduly lenient.
